videos.headline: Houston QB King lasers TD to Stevenson
videos.description: D'Eriq King dials up a 13-yard touchdown strike to Marquez Stevenson to put Houston up first.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Houston QB King lasers TD to Stevenson) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Houston DB lights up WR on huge hit
videos.description: Anthony Gordon completes a pass to Brandon Arconado, who gets drilled by Houston's Glenson Sprewell.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Houston DB lights up WR on huge hit) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington State's Gordon uncorks TD pass
videos.description: Anthony Gordon drops a 39-yard pass into the hands of Easop Winston Jr. for a Cougars' touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington State's Gordon uncorks TD pass) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: King crashes into end zone for a Houston TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King punches in the goal-line touchdown for his second score of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (King crashes into end zone for a Houston TD) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: King ties Tebow for consecutive games with pass, rushing TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King ties Tim Tebow for the most consecutive games (14) with a passing and rushing touchdown with his two scores vs. Washington State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (King ties Tebow for consecutive games with pass, rushing TD) 2019/9/13 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Cougars capitalize with TD on King's fumble
videos.description: Washington State cashes in on a D'Eriq King fumble as Max Borghi takes a carry up the gut for a 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cougars capitalize with TD on King's fumble) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gordon slings deep ball to Patmon for TD
videos.description: Washington State takes a one possession lead on Anthony Gordon's 39-yard touchdown to Dezmon Patmon.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gordon slings deep ball to Patmon for TD) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Leach's trick play backfires on whacky snap
videos.description: Washington State is flagged for an illegal snap as Mike Leach calls a trick play with the ball being snapped by WR Brandon Arconado.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Leach's trick play backfires on whacky snap) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gordon zips 3rd TD pass
videos.description: Anthony Gordon wiggles around in the pocket and fires a 7-yard touchdown to Travell Harris.

videos.headline: King cuts into Cougars' lead with 3rd TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King rushes into the end zone for his third total touchdown of the game as Houston trails by 7 points late.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (King cuts into Cougars' lead with 3rd TD) 2019/9/13 ESHEET
